{"tid":1701480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"到咗今時今日大家唔好再相信香港法治","createTime":"2019-11-09T05:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T07:28:03.000Z","uid":89353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf710de3080e31989a0ae55ef9b21d0d19760779","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家一直都覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">香港法治機構唔搞得</span><br />\n一直集中行政立法<br />\n但其實我哋嘅司法一早<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">名存實亡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲往往罪都會輕啲</span><br />\n今次何君堯一案就話係謀殺<br />\n藍絲襲擊人就話係襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我哋個<span style=\"color: gold;\">律政司又係行政長官任命</span><br />\n佢僭建佢有問題我哋都踢佢唔走<br />\n而佢亦都係司法方面往往幫住行政長官<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗下我哋<span style=\"color: gold;\">每一次上訴每一次判刑</span><br />\n諗下佢哋幫住啲狗比禁制令<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋香港人仲可唔可以相信呢個司法制度</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋香港人係咪應該做啲野</span></span>"},{"pid":"8f83f53e517a3baa5d3868c5ab8d8415e434d579","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01b8368ad9986d77850abec91c40e8bae369cb2b","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eaf2825e39a9d3790ce86c4c4150f70337afc6f","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:02:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a113f66cad0e7b52a0b0b234d938e9cdead91aff","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3835f7818038d426da19f98167c40528ee21893","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c09b61ff9ee398aa49ca937441b9b49dddefe185","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e81fcc90c77b83f662ef1c5ad33a6720f95aae","tid":1701480,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"303cbdf32cbf56e4b02ecdb01dae6db363229b5c","tid":1701480,"uid":306621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"無敵技能：人大釋法<br />\n輔助技能：終院法官特首任命<br />\n結論：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一早無咗法治啦，仲以為有法治根本係戇鳩</span></span>"}]}